  "title": "Operations Supervisor/Executive",
  "description": "<p>Our company imports granite aggregates from China, Thailand, Indonesia and Malaysia for Ready Mix Concrete Production</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We have a fleet of barges and lorries to support our business. We also charter Bulk Carrier for transportation of granite</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are seeking a candidate  to coordinate  and manage our Fleet of lorries including contractors lorries from Johore and in Singapore and barging logistics operations at Jurong Port and at Pulau Punggol Aggregate Terminal where granites aggregate are unloaded from our barges</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Experience in supply chain management either in construction, marine barge operation, or the transportation industry is a plus</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Both experienced and inexperienced applicants are welcome to apply.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you are hardworking and possess a positive work attitude, you may be the ideal candidate for us.</p>",
